                     <note type="paleography">Written along the fibers in medium sized ligatured letters. The hand is expert and clear. The scribe irregularly dipped his pen into the ink maybe to correct mistaken letters. A couple small dots can be seen between line at the middle and before the end of the document. The interlinear spaces are not even: (0.5 cm) at the beginning of the text, (0.3 cm) at the middle and (0.5 cm) at the end. No abbreviations are attested.</note>
